data.description: Beautiful and spacious home perfect for entertaining! Take a look this inviting home on large 1/2 acre lot! Home features large living room, hardwood & tile floors, crown molding, chefs kitchen and spacious master with full on suite bath! This home boast outdoor living at its finest with large covered porch, fenced area with fire pit and above ground pool for hot summer days! Outside there is also a storm shelter, RV Hookup with 30 and 50 AMP service, and 2 out buildings to store you lawn mower, side by side and yard tools! Call today for more information or to schedule your property tour today!
